{
  "stem": "7832.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we had just come in from the zahlappell.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We were out there for like four hours in the rain and-- and-- and mud and everything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we were ordered to go out again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they took us out to the front of the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It was so close to the crematorium that the ashes were falling on the ground where we were.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And they ordered us to sit on the-- on the ground.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We sat in the hot ashes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And the ashes from the crematorium were coming down like-- like little-- little drizzles of-- of rain on us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And they told us they were gonna give us a concert to celebrate the holidays.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And so 32,000 women or less, after they had taken some away, sat on the ground in the hot ashes, the-- all crematoriums, all seven of them were burning like you would never.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "The flames and the ashes were unbearable.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "The stench from the bodies-- it was such a gray day even though it wasn't raining anymore.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "It was like night time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "It was like so dark.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And there was this platform in front of us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And all these beautiful women in crisp uniforms with make-up and lipstick and blonde, long hair-- we had no hair.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "But they were-- they came up and these-- these SS men, young guys, strong, well-fed, well-preserved with-- with clean clothes, sipping something.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "You know, either they had a cup or they had something wrapped up and they were eating, and they were laughing and talking to one another, having a great time.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And we're sitting there, motionless.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "We were supposed to sit and just watch them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And then now the band came.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "The band came up on this platform-- little children in striped uniforms.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
